    {
      "id": "E:note:row427484:1",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Mr. [**Known lastname 3957**] is a 74 year old male with a history of ulcerative",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row427484#s1",
      "text": "Mr. [**Known lastname 3957**] is a 74 year old male with a history of ulcerative colitis    now on prolonged immunosuppressive therapy, coronary artery disease and    non-small cell lung cancer s/p VATs and left upper lobectomy in    [**2146-11-4**] who is transferred to the ICU for increasing oxygen    requirements and tacypnea.Patient was continued on solumedrol and also    given cyclosporine."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row427484:2",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Also found to have left DVT and started heparin    and bridged to coumadin.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row427484#s2",
      "text": "Also found to have left DVT and started heparin    and bridged to coumadin."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row427484:3",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "On [**12-5**], decreased oxygen saturation and    dyspnea.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row427484#s3",
      "text": "On [**12-5**], decreased oxygen saturation and    dyspnea."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row427484:4",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "CT scan on [**12-6**] revealed left hydropneumothorax and also    bilateral infi",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row427484#s4",
      "text": "CT scan on [**12-6**] revealed left hydropneumothorax and also    bilateral infiltrates consistent with multi-focal pneumonia."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row427484:5",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Started    on levofloxacin and flagyl and then started Vancomycin and zosyn [**1",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row427484#s5",
      "text": "Started    on levofloxacin and flagyl and then started Vancomycin and zosyn [**12-7**]    Over past 48 hours, oxygenation has worsened."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row427484:6",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Also, had drop in    hematocrit from 27 to 22 this am.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row427484#s6",
      "text": "Also, had drop in    hematocrit from 27 to 22 this am."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row427484:7",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Transfused with 2 units prbc.",
      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row427484#s7",
      "text": "Transfused with 2 units prbc."
    },
    {
      "id": "E:note:row427484:8",
      "kind": "note_sentence",
      "display": "Delirium / confusion    Assessment:    Difficult to assess at times d/t tachypne",
      "code": null,
